location.fullValue: The Pietra Plan, Arvada at Stonefield

data.description: Lovely single story home with 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage & 1570 sq ft. This home boasts a great room with lots of natural light and high ceilings. The kitchen offers plenty of cabinets, upgraded counter tops and SS appliances including the fridge. The Primary bedroom is tucked away in the rear of the home and separated from the secondary bedrooms for privacy. The fully landscaped front yard is maintained and watered by the HOA. The backyard is a blank slate for new owners to put their own touch on it! Agents please see private remarks.
